## Animation Guidelines

### Micro-interactions
- Subtle scale on hover (1.02-1.05)
- Smooth transitions (0.3s ease)
- Gentle opacity changes
- Button state animations

### Scroll Animations
- Parallax effects for hero images
- Fade-in-up for content sections
- Stagger animations for lists
- Smooth scroll behavior

## Image Treatment
1. **Hero Images**
   - Full-width, high-resolution
